  <div class="container">
    <h1>Using Crystals for Wealth and Prosperity</h1>
    <p>Crystals have been used for centuries to attract wealth, success, and abundance. Here are some popular crystals for manifesting financial prosperity and how you can use them to align with your financial goals.</p>

    <div class="crystal-section">
      <h2>Citrine (Stone of Success)</h2>
      <p>Citrine, known as the "Merchant’s Stone," is often associated with attracting wealth and success. It helps foster creativity, which is useful for finding new business ideas and opportunities.</p>
      <p><strong>How to Use:</strong> Keep citrine in your wallet, cash box, or workspace to encourage financial energy.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="crystal-section">
      <h2>Pyrite (Fool’s Gold)</h2>
      <p>With its gold-like shine, pyrite symbolizes prosperity and wealth. It is believed to attract money and support financial strength.</p>
      <p><strong>How to Use:</strong> Place pyrite on your desk or in your home office to attract abundance.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="crystal-section">
      <h2>Green Aventurine (Stone of Opportunity)</h2>
      <p>Known as the "Stone of Opportunity," green aventurine is linked to luck and wealth, making it ideal for new ventures.</p>
      <p><strong>How to Use:</strong> Carry it during job interviews or financial meetings to encourage prosperity.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="crystal-section">
      <h2>Jade (Stone of Harmony)</h2>
      <p>Jade is a powerful stone of balance, harmony, and financial stability. It’s often used to bring about wise decision-making.</p>
      <p><strong>How to Use:</strong> Place jade in your “wealth corner” (southeast area of your home) according to Feng Shui.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="crystal-section">
      <h2>Clear Quartz (Master Healer)</h2>
      <p>Clear quartz amplifies energy and is versatile, enhancing the effects of other wealth-attracting crystals.</p>
      <p><strong>How to Use:</strong> Place clear quartz with other money crystals to boost their effects, or use it during meditation to reinforce financial goals.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tips">
      <h2>Tips for Using Crystals to Attract Wealth</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Create a Wealth Altar:</strong> Set up a small space for your wealth crystals with other prosperity symbols like coins or a plant.</li>
        <li><strong>Set Intentions:</strong> Cleanse your crystals, then set a specific intention like “I attract financial stability and success” before placing them.</li>
        <li><strong>Visualization Practice:</strong> Hold a crystal during meditation and visualize achieving your financial goals, imagining the success in vivid detail.</li>
        <li><strong>Crystal-Infused Water:</strong> For crystals like clear quartz, create crystal-infused water and use it to sprinkle around areas where you manage finances.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

